  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_janosh</Cell><Cell>Send for Janosh.</Cell><Cell>ヤノシュを呼んでくれ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_janosh</Cell><Cell>I see you are a true gourmand.</Cell><Cell>なるほど、本物の美食家だな。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>ui_mercenary_custom_mathew</Cell><Cell>Mathew the Collector (500 groschen).</Cell><Cell>収集家のマテウス（500グロッシェン）。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_mathew</Cell><Cell>I want Mathew the Collector.</Cell><Cell>収集家のマテウスが欲しい。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_mathew</Cell><Cell>I see you want the entire Devil's pack.</Cell><Cell>悪魔の一味を全員集めたいわけだな。</Cell></Row>

