  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_type_return</Cell><Cell>Consider it done. I'll send a runner right away.</Cell><Cell>任せろ。すぐに伝令を出す。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>ui_mercenary_heal_yourselves</Cell><Cell>Patch yourselves up.</Cell><Cell>手当てをしろ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_heal_henry_1</Cell><Cell>Take these supplies and patch yourselves up. You look terrible.</Cell><Cell>この物資を使って手当てをしろ。酷い顔をしているぞ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_heal_merc</Cell><Cell>We'll do what we can, boss, but a proper healer wouldn't go amiss.</Cell><Cell>できる限りやりますが、親分、ちゃんとした治療師がいてくれると助かりますね。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_info_merc_healed</Cell><Cell>Your mercenaries have been healed.</Cell><Cell>傭兵たちが回復した。</Cell></Row>


  <Row><Cell>merc_test_bark_string</Cell><Cell>This is a test. I like cheese.</Cell><Cell>これはテストです。チーズが好きです。</Cell></Row>
  
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_1_1</Cell><Cell>Soon as I scrape together enough Groschen...</Cell><Cell>グロッシェンが十分貯まったら…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_1_2</Cell><Cell>I'm buying a little freehold.</Cell><Cell>小さな自由保有地を買うんだ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_1_3</Cell><Cell>Sit on my arse all day...</Cell><Cell>一日中ぼーっとして…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_1_4</Cell><Cell>Watch the serfs do the heavy lifting.</Cell><Cell>農奴どもが重労働するのを眺めるんだ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_1_5</Cell><Cell>Just me, the sheep, and a full belly.</Cell><Cell>俺と羊と、腹いっぱいの飯だけ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_1_6</Cell><Cell>Christ, that'll be the life.</Cell><Cell>神様、それが本当の人生ってもんだ。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_2_1</Cell><Cell>Just one more year in this bloody trade.</Cell><Cell>この血塗られた稼業もあと一年だ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_2_2</Cell><Cell>Then I'm buying that empty plot down in Horschan...</Cell><Cell>そしたらホルシャンの空き地を買うんだ…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_2_3</Cell><Cell>Finally get some peace and quiet.</Cell><Cell>やっと静かな暮らしができる。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_2_4</Cell><Cell>I'll hang my sword in the rafters...</Cell><Cell>剣は梁に吊るして…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_2_5</Cell><Cell>Let the damn thing rust to dust.</Cell><Cell>あの忌々しい物を錆びるまで放っておく。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_2_6</Cell><Cell>Maybe brew my own ale.</Cell><Cell>自分でエールでも醸造するか。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_2_7</Cell><Cell>Drink myself to sleep every night... heheh.</Cell><Cell>毎晩飲んだくれて眠るんだ…へへへ。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_3_1</Cell><Cell>I still remember it... before I was a man grown.</Cell><Cell>今でも覚えている…まだ子供だった頃のことを。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_3_2</Cell><Cell>My father's farm.</Cell><Cell>親父の農場だ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_3_3</Cell><Cell>A sturdy house. Had a red door.</Cell><Cell>頑丈な家だった。赤い扉があった。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_3_4</Cell><Cell>Then those Cuman bastards came.</Cell><Cell>そこへあのクマンの野郎どもが来た。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_3_5</Cell><Cell>Slaughtered them like pigs... only I got away into the woods.</Cell><Cell>豚のように皆殺しにされた…俺だけが森へ逃げ込んだ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_3_6</Cell><Cell>Been living by the sword ever since.</Cell><Cell>それからはずっと剣で生きてきた。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_farm_3_7</Cell><Cell>Maybe one day... I'll go back and rebuild it.</Cell><Cell>いつかは…戻って建て直せるかもしれない。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_1_1</Cell><Cell>Lord, what a night that was...</Cell><Cell>神様、あの夜は最高だったな…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_1_2</Cell><Cell>Zdena, her name was...</Cell><Cell>ズデナというんだ…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_1_3</Cell><Cell>Hair like spun gold...</Cell><Cell>紡いだ金のような髪…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_1_4</Cell><Cell>Breasts as soft as rising dough...</Cell><Cell>発酵する生地のように柔らかな胸…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_1_5</Cell><Cell>I'd fight the Devil himself for another night with her.</Cell><Cell>もう一晩あいつと過ごせるなら、悪魔とだって戦ってみせる。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_2_1</Cell><Cell>It's been too long...</Cell><Cell>もう長すぎる…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_2_2</Cell><Cell>Since I felt the warmth of a woman's skin...</Cell><Cell>女の温もりを感じてからもう随分になる…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_2_3</Cell><Cell>Every tavern we hit, it's nothing but toothless old hags.</Cell><Cell>どの酒場に行っても歯のないばあさんばかりだ。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_2_4</Cell><Cell>A man has needs, damn it.</Cell><Cell>男には欲求ってものがあるんだ、まったく。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_3_1</Cell><Cell>Every time I think of Betti, my heart skips a beat...</Cell><Cell>ベッティのことを思うたびに、胸が締め付けられる…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_3_2</Cell><Cell>I like to think she's still waiting by the hearth.</Cell><Cell>今も暖炉のそばで待っていると思いたい。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_3_3</Cell><Cell>Mending my tunic...</Cell><Cell>俺のチュニックを繕いながら…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_3_4</Cell><Cell>Watching the villagers go about their day...</Cell><Cell>村人たちの日々を眺めながら…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_3_5</Cell><Cell>But then I remember... it was my knife that ended up in her chest.</Cell><Cell>だがそこで思い出す…あいつの胸に刺さったのは俺のナイフだということを。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_3_6</Cell><Cell>*sighs heavily*</Cell><Cell>*重くため息をつく*</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_4_1</Cell><Cell>Barely a fortnight since I left my Danka...</Cell><Cell>ダンカと別れてからまだ二週間も経っていない…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_4_2</Cell><Cell>Wept her eyes dry when I rode off.</Cell><Cell>俺が馬で去るとき、泣きはらしていた。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_4_3</Cell><Cell>That bastard Sigismund... tearing families apart.</Cell><Cell>あのジギスムントの野郎め…家族を引き裂きやがって。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_4_4</Cell><Cell>Now I'm stuck in this godforsaken mud-hole!</Cell><Cell>それで今、この神に見捨てられた泥沼に嵌まっている！</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_4_5</Cell><Cell>Just trying to earn enough coin to go back to her...</Cell><Cell>あいつのところへ戻れるだけの金を稼ごうとしているだけなのに…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_4_6</Cell><Cell>But every time we pass an alehouse...</Cell><Cell>だが酒場の前を通るたびに…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_4_7</Cell><Cell>My purse ends up lighter than before.</Cell><Cell>財布が前より軽くなっている。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_5_1</Cell><Cell>My sweet Matilda...</Cell><Cell>俺の可愛いマティルダ…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_5_2</Cell><Cell>Hope she sleeps soundly under that old oak tree.</Cell><Cell>あの古い樫の木の下で安らかに眠れていればいい。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_5_3</Cell><Cell>God's wounds, what a hellish night that was...</Cell><Cell>神よ、あの夜は地獄だった…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_5_4</Cell><Cell>Screamed until her voice gave out.</Cell><Cell>声が枯れるまで叫び続けた。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_5_5</Cell><Cell>The whole village heard her.</Cell><Cell>村中に聞こえていた。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_5_6</Cell><Cell>Had to bury poor little Jan right there beside her.</Cell><Cell>かわいそうなヤンをその場で、あいつの隣に埋めるしかなかった。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_5_7</Cell><Cell>Just an infant...</Cell><Cell>まだ赤子だったのに…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_woman_5_8</Cell><Cell>Couldn't bear to look at the house after that.</Cell><Cell>それからはあの家を見ることすらできなかった。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_1_1</Cell><Cell>Ah, the vineyards of Mělník...</Cell><Cell>ああ、メルニークのぶどう畑…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_1_2</Cell><Cell>Such wine they press!</Cell><Cell>あそこで搾るワインときたら！</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_1_3</Cell><Cell>Red as a ruby.</Cell><Cell>ルビーのように真っ赤で。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_1_4</Cell><Cell>Sweet as sin.</Cell><Cell>罪のように甘い。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_1_5</Cell><Cell>Every Groschen I bleed for...</Cell><Cell>血を流して稼いだグロッシェンは全て…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_1_6</Cell><Cell>Is for just one more drop of that nectar on my tongue.</Cell><Cell>あの甘露をもう一滴、舌に乗せるためにある。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_2_1</Cell><Cell>I can't stomach this!</Cell><Cell>もう我慢できない！</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_2_2</Cell><Cell>Four days without a drop!</Cell><Cell>四日間も一滴も飲んでいない！</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_2_3</Cell><Cell>The whole world makes more sense after a pint.</Cell><Cell>一杯飲めば世界全体がもっとよく見える。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_2_4</Cell><Cell>Pray to God the next tavern isn't far.</Cell><Cell>次の酒場が遠くないよう神に祈るしかない。</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_3_1</Cell><Cell>Where's the spirits?</Cell><Cell>蒸留酒はどこだ？</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_3_2</Cell><Cell>Who hid the damn schnapps?!</Cell><Cell>誰がシュナップスを隠したんだ！？</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_3_3</Cell><Cell>Henry! Did you drink the last flask?</Cell><Cell>ヘンリー！最後のフラスコを飲んだのはお前か？</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_3_4</Cell><Cell>This is absolute torture!</Cell><Cell>これは拷問も同然だ！</Cell></Row>

  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_4_1</Cell><Cell>Beer... I only have to think about it and my knees get weak.</Cell><Cell>ビール…考えるだけで膝が崩れそうになる。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_4_2</Cell><Cell>If wine is Christ's blood, and bread is His body...</Cell><Cell>ワインがキリストの血で、パンが御体なら…</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_4_3</Cell><Cell>Then beer must be His very soul.</Cell><Cell>ビールこそ御魂に違いない。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_dream_drink_4_4</Cell><Cell>Amen to that.</Cell><Cell>アーメン。</Cell></Row>
  

  
  
  

</Table>